$Module zstd 3 "Vinyl Fetch Processor for zstd de-/compression"

$ABI vrt

$Synopsis manual

SYNOPSIS
========

::

  import zstd;

DESCRIPTION
===========

VFP zstd is a Vinyl Fetch Processor to support the zstd
compression algorithm for responses fetched from backends. The VFP
integrates Vinyl with the `zstd library`_.

$Event event

$Function STRING version()
Returns the version of the underlying libzstd library.